              <strong>New to Zurich and have quick insurance questions?</strong> <a href="/ai-chat" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:underline">Chat with our AI Insurance Assistant</a> for instant answers! For more personalized guidance, <a href="/free-consultation" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:underline">Schedule a Free Consultation</a> today!
            </p>
